data.description: Lots of space in this well maintained split foyer home. Perfect for a growing family! The Great Room features an eye catching stone fireplace and a vaulted ceiling for a dramatic look. A separate dining space can be viewed from the kitchen which features stainless steel appliances and pantry. The Master Bedroom is separated from the secondary bedrooms for maximum privacy. In addition to a lovely bay window with nearly new carpet. The Master bathroom features a separate tub and shower with a window above the garden tub. The secondary bedrooms are oversized and have large closets. A large finished room downstairs is perfect for a recreational area or an additional bedroom. Low maintenance vinyl siding and a large level lot make for easy living in this home.
